import React from 'react'
import { Divider, Toolbar, Typography, Box, Grid, Paper, Link } from '@mui/material'
import { styled } from '@mui/system'

// Feature Box Styling
const FeatureBox = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
  borderRadius: '10px',
  boxShadow: '0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)',
  padding: theme.spacing(4),
  textAlign: 'center',
  backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)', // Transparent background
  transition: 'transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease',
  '&:hover': {
    transform: 'translateY(-10px)',
    boxShadow: '0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)',
  },
}))

// Updated Footer Styling
const Footer = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({
  backgroundColor: '#1c1c1c', // Darker background for a more professional look
  color: 'white',
  padding: theme.spacing(6, 0), // Top and bottom padding
  marginTop: theme.spacing(4),
  borderRadius: '10px',
  boxShadow: '0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)', // Deeper shadow for more depth
  textAlign: 'center',
  fontFamily: '"Roboto", sans-serif',
}))

// Footer Columns Styling
const FooterColumn = styled(Grid)(({ theme }) => ({
  display: 'flex',
  flexDirection: 'column',
  alignItems: 'flex-start',
  justifyContent: 'center',
  textAlign: 'left', // Align text to the left
  paddingLeft: theme.spacing(3), // Padding for text alignment
  paddingRight: theme.spacing(3),
}))

// Link Styling inside Footer for better interaction
const FooterLink = styled(Link)(({ theme }) => ({
  color: 'white',
  textDecoration: 'none',
  '&:hover': {
    color: '#f4a261', // Light color on hover for contrast
    textDecoration: 'underline',
  },
}))

export default function Home() {
  return (
    <>
      {/* Toolbar */}
      <Toolbar>
        <Typography 
          variant='h5' 
          sx={{
            fontWeight: 'bold',
            color: '#000',
            textTransform: 'uppercase',
            letterSpacing: 2,
          }}
        >
          Features of My Bank
        </Typography>
      </Toolbar>
      <Divider />

      {/* Feature Boxes Section */}
      <Box sx={{ padding: 4, display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-around' }}>
        <Grid container spacing={3} justifyContent="center">
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <FeatureBox>
              <Typography variant="h6">Easy Transactions</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2">Make seamless transfers and manage your bank accounts with ease.</Typography>
            </FeatureBox>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <FeatureBox>
              <Typography variant="h6">24/7 Support</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2">Our customer support team is available around the clock to assist you.</Typography>
            </FeatureBox>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <FeatureBox>
              <Typography variant="h6">Secure Banking</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2">Your account security is our priority, with top-notch encryption.</Typography>
            </FeatureBox>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>

      {/* Footer Section */}
      <Footer>
        <Grid container spacing={6}>
          {/* About Section */}
          <FooterColumn item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <Typography variant="h6" style={{ fontWeight: 'bold', marginBottom: 16 }}>
              About
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2">
              Learn more about our history, mission, and values. We are committed to providing excellent banking services with a focus on customer satisfaction.
            </Typography>
          </FooterColumn>
          
          {/* Contact Section */}
          <FooterColumn item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <Typography variant="h6" style={{ fontWeight: 'bold', marginBottom: 16 }}>
              Contact
            </Typography>
            <FooterLink href="mailto:support@mybank.com">Email Us</FooterLink>
            <FooterLink href="tel:+123456789" style={{ marginTop: 8 }}>Call Us</FooterLink>
          </FooterColumn>
        </Grid>
        <Divider sx={{ margin: '20px 0', backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)' }} />
        <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ fontSize: '0.875rem' }}>
          © 2025 My Bank. All Rights Reserved.
        </Typography>
      </Footer>
    </>
  )
}
